text: Garry Roque (born 14 April 1960) is a Canadian equestrian. He competed in two events at the 2004 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1960 births Category:Living people Category:Bermudian male equestrians Category:Canadian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Canada Category:Equestrians at the 2004 Summer Olympics Category:People from Paget Parish
